about_us_text: In accordance with the Decree of the Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Joint Stock Company "Uzbekistan Railways" No. 897 dated October 10, 2023, the Joint Stock Company "Temiryo'lekspress" was established. The Joint Stock Company "Temiryo'lekspress" provides technical and technological and passenger services on 6 high-speed "Afrosiyob" electric trains.

contact_page.content: Submit your application in the name of "Uzbekistan Railways" JSC https://pm.gov.uz/uz through section 2 of the virtual lobby of the President of the Republic of Uzbekistan "SCHEDULE OF RECEIVING CITIZENS AND ADDRESSES OF MINISTERS AND HEADS OF OFFICES" You can select the position of "Uzbekistan Railways" JSC from "Unions and joint-stock companies"
